title: Puppy_Linux_Fatdog64-630_11-Feb-2014
description:
Fatdog64-630 Final (February 11 2014)

from/more at <a href=" http://www.murga-linux.com/puppy/viewtopic.php?t=91937" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.murga-linux.com/puppy/viewtopic.php?t=91937</a>

Kirk and James are pleased to announce the release of Fatdog 630 Final. 

 This release marks the fourth, and probably last, release of the Fatdog 600 series and comes with a lot of improvements over the last release, Fatdog64-621. 

 Get it from http://distro.ibiblio.org/fatdog/iso. 

 For those who are new to Fatdog, please read the  Frequently asked Questions and Answers (FAQs) to save yourself from headache (the same documents are also included in the ISO on the browser home page).
